SELECT COALESCE("t"."Id", "t"."Id") AS "Id", "t"."PostTypeId" AS "POSTTYPEID", "t"."Id0", "Votes"."Id" AS "Id1", "t"."CreationDate", CASE WHEN CAST("Votes"."VoteTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "FD_COL_5", CASE WHEN CAST("Votes"."VoteTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "FD_COL_6"
